Use `redo` to build.

The build scripts assume that libtcod v1.5.0 is available in ./libtcod-1.5.0

To run, you might need to add LD_LIBRARY_PATH=./libtcod-1.5.0 to the command.

libtcod is available at: http://doryen.eptalys.net/libtcod/download/

Lore - Contains all of the game data: maps, items, etc.
Kobold - The 3D engine
Goblin - The 2D engine
